@startuml
skinparam activity {
    BackgroundColor<<future>> #FFF4E6
    BorderColor<<future>> #C47F36
    BorderStyle<<future>> dashed
}

start

:Extract 10 years of legacy enquiry,\nfeedback, citizen, and file data; <<future>>

:Profile source data for volume,\nquality, duplicate citizens,\nmissing channels, and file references; <<future>>

:Map records to Contact, Case,\nContentVersion, ContentDocumentLink,\nand Migration_Batch__c; <<future>>

:Cleanse and deduplicate citizens\nusing phone, email, and national ID\nwhere available; <<future>>

:Load reference data and users,\nroles, queues, divisions, and metadata; <<future>>

:Pilot load representative sample\nand reconcile counts; <<future>>

if (Pilot accepted?) then (Yes)
    :Bulk load 6M historical Case records\nin controlled batches; <<future>>

    :Upload 100GB historical files\nas Salesforce Files or external archive links\nbased on storage assessment; <<future>>

    :Reconcile record counts,\nfile links, ownership, sharing,\nand audit fields; <<future>>

    :Freeze legacy writes,\nperform delta migration,\nand complete cutover; <<future>>
else (No)
    :Fix mapping, cleansing,\nor storage approach; <<future>>
    stop
endif

:Post-migration validation,\nreport certification, and rollback checkpoint; <<future>>

stop

legend right
  |= Style |= Meaning |
  |<#FFF4E6> Amber activity | Future historical migration plan |
endlegend

@enduml
